column5: Hi folks.  I've been a member of this fantastic site a number of years ago but life gets in the way sometimes and ...........  Anyhow, my name is Brian and I am glad to be back.  I very recently moved from Ontario to Fort McMurray AB and hope soon to discover what this area has for fishing and hunting.  Thanks for taking the time to read my brief introduction and hope to be reporting soon.  Tight Lines!!!
Welcome back aboard!  Looking forward to some reports from your neck of the woods.
Good lists and lots of pics from the top locations. Lots and lots of fish porn. Please.
Welcome to the board, good on you for goin' fishin' up in Fort Macmoney. It is a lot better than the alternative activities  there.....
